<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.4">
<l>maṇaṅkaḷ nāṟum vārku ḻalār mātar kaḷātarattai</l>
<l>puṇarnta cintaip puṉmai yāḷaṉ poṉṟa varicilaiyāl</l>
<l>kaṇaṅka ḷuṇṇa vāḷi yāṇṭa kāva laṉukkiḷaiyōṉ</l>
<l>kuṇaṅkaḷ pāṭi yāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Singing of the virtues of the younger brother of the protector</l>
<l>Who used arrows so that the vile one perished,</l>
<l>[His] thoughts embraced desire for ladies with long hair</l>
<l rend="indent">where fragrance wafts,</l>
<l>Since he consumed the hordes [of demons] with a striped bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">we are dancing to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
